Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本作品是假定首都圈内发生强烈地震，\N以大量的研究和验证为基础制作的虚构故事。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了追求真实性，我们在构造原创故事时已做\N过很多模拟，但在演出上仍会有与真实情况不符之处。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:01:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是浓烟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是在做梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那个大姐姐去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道 别什么事都来问姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 实在不行就我们两个也能回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 看看手机现在能不能打通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈没受伤就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 爸爸妈妈没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道 又没跟他们联系上！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你说了别什么事都来问我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 二位想必肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子一饿 就很容易着急上火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫真理就行了 悠贵君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来你也吃点吧 还有饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是怎么来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:04:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来非常时期便利店会派发食物 就去看了看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们醒来一看你不在 还以为你先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见我没在 未来觉得寂寞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们来约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起 我不会一个人到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有事要离开你们 也一定会告诉你们去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对我们这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家里不还有孩子在等你回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是陪着我们 你不是能更早回到家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就像你说的这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们住的方向相同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这也是一种缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一起走到哪就一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗 我们只会拖累你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿着 把这个吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:05:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿的时候 人就会变得消极
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱后有了精神 加油走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 吃饭吧吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是梅干馅 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的馅是鲑鱼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真是热啊 哎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是个大热天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该有四十度了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理小姐真像大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 虽然我经常被人这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是未来 你说得太直白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别 别这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认输了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好昨天你去买了饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 来看看新闻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看太久的话就没电了 看一下下就关咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（正在获得数据）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（选台中）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在再次播报因地震造成的都内受灾情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有交通都暂停运行 还没有恢复的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实施了第一交通管制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多摩川 国道246号线以及7环以内的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是全面禁止车辆通行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截至目前 共确认死亡人数843人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:07:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并有大量失踪 重伤者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后 这个数字还会增加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然死了这么多人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一部分火灾现在还在蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在火灾现场附近的各位请立刻前往避难所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且现在很多受灾群众正在步行回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对今后的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请京坂大学灾害研究所的村田宪昭教授来说明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因这次首都的直下型地震造成回家困难的人数
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据估计超过了650万人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后余震将持续到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计震级5级以上的余震会持续三天左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往回家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然大家都在走着回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这状况 也不知道电车什么时候再开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐 我们也走着回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了饭团 现在有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们家在世田谷 很远的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 确实不是轻轻松松就能走到的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台场被孤立了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥都被烧了 到处也都出不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们不是糟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里会沉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 这么大片地是沉不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但台场是填海造出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这边有阴凉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真担心 我们既没水也没食物…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 也有人住在这附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就会有人来救援了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对 还好我们一家都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也想尽早回爸爸妈妈那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是海上保安厅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在通过水上巴士运送受灾群众
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从台场到日出栈桥方面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请到彩虹公园旁边的栈桥集合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到千叶方面的人请…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 看来能坐船到日出栈桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不该穿凉鞋来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚磨破了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 看了就痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等 我们家有小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创可贴可是必备的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是青蛙的哦姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐是青蛙星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙星人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 你别乱说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 要实在不行了我就背着你走 呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要背你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过难受的时候还是要说出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会背你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对自己腰腿力还是很有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己能走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就是这股劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接着走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚还疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要着急 别勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我们真的能坐到船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多人要上船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 坐不到船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之去看看吧 估计应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理小姐真够乐观的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要说是积极啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 一～二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了 真是太谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你也来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能跟妈妈走散了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能到码头了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐姐真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也可以说是多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是刚说好了离开我们的时候 要跟我们说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐姐是在做好事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往东京国际展示场的人请直走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要乘船到滨松町方面的人 请在前面的十字路口左转
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想回去的人都往这个方向来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心别走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来也来牵着手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用了 又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要好好跟上哦 别走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真理小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真碍事 快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 真理小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别在这种地方停下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是牵着手走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放开手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像爆炸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高速居然崩塌了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 过桥太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能坐船了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本船现在开始救助落水者 请去乘坐水上巴士！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要上这艘船！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能放开手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船即将出发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让比较虚弱的人先上船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是等下一艘船吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要乘船的人请等下一艘船！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的两个孩子快上船！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 这位妈妈也快上船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 啊 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等下一艘船！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 很危险的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烂透了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽说不是现在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 总之还是坐上船了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是会钻空子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家一叫你这位妈妈 就那么爽快地应了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实自从丈夫去世后 我越来越坚强了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己一个人也要好好把小雏养大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看 桥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在烧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是油罐车起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 人掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是晚一步 上了那艘船的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 我们这边也来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们在那艘船上的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 让你们遇到这种危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 真理小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京塔倒塌 救援队正奋力进行救援
